reviewText:
C'mon. Is there anyone on the planet buying this for a reason other than the Beatles? We've all seen it. Here it is in pristine quality.
4 stars instead of 5 because the other acts and the commercials lose their novelty value real fast. They must've shown the same Pillsbury ad 17 times. And the other acts.are bad, like real bad. The unintentional humor turns to cringe inducing awkwardness by the start of the 2nd episode.
